      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is recommended primarily for those looking for a dedicated project car or a reliable source for spare parts. The exterior shows substantial wear, including significant body damage, deep scratches, and visible rust patches on several panels. Mechanically, the car requires immediate attention; it currently runs but has noticeable engine trouble and a worn suspension system. Inside, the upholstery is heavily stained and torn in several places. Buyers should expect to invest considerable time and resources into repairs to make this vehicle roadworthy again.",
