      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really great shape, running smoothly and ready for many more miles. It's been well-cared for and is perfect for anyone who wants a dependable vehicle that looks good on the road. I've absolutely loved driving this beauty, and I'm sure you will too! Drop me a message if you'd like to come see it!",
