      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I'm parting with my car and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smooth, and has been really well-loved. It's perfect if you're looking for a dependable daily driver that still has plenty of life left in it. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
