      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2005 BMW M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. This chassis has been properly sorted with rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure timing accuracy and VANOS oil pump longevity. The suspension retains its factory-tuned geometry with updated bushings for precise turn-in. While showing honest cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are strong, with recent rod bearing service completed as preventative maintenance. A mechanically sound icon ready for the B-roads.",
